### ============================================================
### FASE 5 — PRODUCTO
### ============================================================

### 8. Crear variante de producto (tenant)
### Guarda el product_variant_id devuelto en @variantId
### NOTA: cabys_code es opcional (FK nullable). Solo incluirlo si el CABYS loader fue ejecutado.
POST {{baseUrl}}/product
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "products": [
    {
      "tenant_id": "{{tenantId}}",
      "sku": "PROD-001",
      "variant_name": "Cuaderno universitario 100 hojas",
      "unit_price": 1500,
      "cabys_code": "0111100009900"
    }
  ]
}


### ============================================================
### FASE 6 — VENTA COMPLETA
### ============================================================
### Cálculo de montos (IVA 13%):
###   unit_price = 1500 CRC
###   quantity   = 2
###   subtotal   = 3000.00
###   impuesto   = 3000 * 0.13 = 390.00
###   total      = 3000 + 390 = 3390.00

### 9. Crear venta completa (sale + items + pagos en un solo request)
# Respuesta: { sale_id, ... }
# → Guardar sale_id en @saleId
POST {{baseUrl}}/sale
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "branch_id": "{{branchId}}",
  "currency_id": 1,
  "tenant_id": "{{tenantId}}",
  "tenant_customer_id": "{{customerId}}",
  "sale_condition": "01",
  "sale_date": "2025-06-01T10:30:00.000Z",
  "subtotal_amount": 3000.00,
  "tax_amount": 390.00,
  "total_amount": 3390.00,
  "is_completed": true,
  "has_electronic_invoice": false,
  "items": [
    {
      "tenant_id": "{{tenantId}}",
      "product_variant_id": "{{variantId}}",
      "quantity": 2,
      "unit_price": 1500.00,
      "total_price": 3000.00
    }
  ],
  "payments": [
    {
      "tenant_customer_id": "{{customerId}}",
      "payment_method_id": 1,
      "is_points_redemption": false,
      "points_redeemed": 0,
      "points_to_currency_rate": 0,
      "payment_amount": 3390.00,
      "payment_date": "2025-06-01T10:30:00.000Z",
      "currency_id": 1,
      "verified": true
    }
  ]
}


### ============================================================
### FASE 7 — CONSULTAR FACTURA DIGITAL
### ============================================================

### 10. Obtener todas las ventas de la sucursal
GET {{baseUrl}}/sale/{{branchId}}


### 11. Obtener facturas del tenant
# Devuelve digital_sale_invoice generada tras la venta
GET {{baseUrl}}/invoice/{{tenantId}}


### 12. Obtener detalle de factura por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/invoice/details/{{saleId}}


### 13. Obtener facturas de un cliente por documento
GET {{baseUrl}}/invoice?id={{tenantId}}&doc=106780001


### ============================================================
### FASE 8 — FACTURA ELECTRÓNICA (e-invoice)
### ============================================================
### La generación de la factura electrónica se dispara automáticamente
### desde SaleService cuando has_electronic_invoice: true en POST /sale.
### No se requiere un endpoint HTTP separado en el módulo e-invoice.
###
### Flujo interno en SaleService.createFullSale():
###   1. INSERT sale con has_electronic_invoice = false
###   2. INSERT sale_items
###   3. INSERT customer_payments
###   4. INSERT digital_sale_invoice  (InvoiceService.createInvoice)
###   5. IF has_electronic_invoice → EInvoiceService.createEInvoiceForSale()
###        → valida venta completada + factura digital existente
###        → genera XML con XmlGeneratorEngine
###        → firma con p12 (EINVOICE_P12_BASE64 + EINVOICE_P12_PASSWORD)
###        → INSERT electronic_sale_invoice
###        → INSERT electronic_sale_invoice_items
###        → UPDATE sale SET has_electronic_invoice = true
###
### Prerequisito: variables de entorno configuradas en .env:
###   EINVOICE_P12_BASE64=<base64 del archivo .p12>
###   EINVOICE_P12_PASSWORD=<contraseña del .p12>

### 14. Venta CON factura electrónica (requiere .p12 configurado en .env)
POST {{baseUrl}}/sale
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "branch_id": "{{branchId}}",
  "currency_id": 1,
  "tenant_id": "{{tenantId}}",
  "tenant_customer_id": "{{customerId}}",
  "sale_condition": "01",
  "sale_date": "2025-06-02T10:30:00.000Z",
  "subtotal_amount": 3000.00,
  "tax_amount": 390.00,
  "total_amount": 3390.00,
  "is_completed": true,
  "has_electronic_invoice": true,
  "items": [
    {
      "tenant_id": "{{tenantId}}",
      "product_variant_id": "{{variantId}}",
      "quantity": 2,
      "unit_price": 1500.00,
      "total_price": 3000.00
    }
  ],
  "payments": [
    {
      "tenant_customer_id": "{{customerId}}",
      "payment_method_id": 1,
      "is_points_redemption": false,
      "points_redeemed": 0,
      "points_to_currency_rate": 0,
      "payment_amount": 3390.00,
      "payment_date": "2025-06-02T10:30:00.000Z",
      "currency_id": 1,
      "verified": true
    }
  ]
}


