### ============================================================
### FASE 11 — VENTA MULTI-ÍTEM CON FACTURA ELECTRÓNICA
### ============================================================
### Prerequisitos:
###   - Variables @v02Id … @v11Id llenadas con los IDs del paso 20
###   - EINVOICE_P12_BASE64 y EINVOICE_P12_PASSWORD en .env
###   - Todos los productos con cabys_code válido (FE requiere CABYS)
###
### Cálculo (IVA 13% sobre todos los ítems):
###   Ítem 01: 10 × @v02Id  @  400  =   4,000
###   Ítem 02:  2 × @v03Id  @ 8,900 =  17,800
###   Ítem 03:  5 × @v04Id  @ 1,200 =   6,000
###   Ítem 04:  4 × @v05Id  @ 2,500 =  10,000
###   Ítem 05:  1 × @v06Id  @ 4,800 =   4,800
###   Ítem 06:  6 × @v07Id  @  700  =   4,200
###   Ítem 07:  1 × @v08Id  @ 6,500 =   6,500
###   Ítem 08:  8 × @v09Id  @  800  =   6,400
###   Ítem 09:  2 × @v10Id  @ 3,200 =   6,400
###   Ítem 10:  3 × @v11Id  @ 1,100 =   3,300
###   ─────────────────────────────────────────
###   subtotal_amount = 69,400.00 CRC
###   tax_amount      = 69,400 × 0.13 = 9,022.00 CRC
###   total_amount    = 78,422.00 CRC
###
### → Guardar sale_id en @multiSaleId

